475
00:31:03,153 --> 00:31:04,820
Hello.

476
00:31:04,821 --> 00:31:07,448
Adakah anjing saya Genius di sini?

477
00:31:07,449 --> 00:31:08,450
Hei, Genius!

478
00:31:09,409 --> 00:31:11,577
Genius!

479
00:31:11,578 --> 00:31:14,705
